data.title: Basic - 7 Days
data.meta_description:
Your dog spends his/her entire day with us, 24 hrs/7 days, going through 1-on-1 expert training sessions. 
Customized program to meet your needs as well as the needs of your dog.
Training requires time, commitment, and consistency that most of us do not have on a daily basis.
Our exclusive program will give you the results you always wanted. Send your dog to our 'camp' style program where they get to socialize with dog members from my pack and utilize pack mentality to learn better dog obedience from them.

Program covers:
1. Basic On Leash Obedience
2. Behavior Modification
3. House Manners
4. Socialization (limited)

No Reinforcement Classes
Program Price:  $1425.00
